4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior knowledge, enabling them to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Students will gain a foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp includes risk management training focused on data loss prevention and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop